com.nokia.dempsy
Class Dempsy

java.lang.Object
  com.nokia.dempsy.Dempsy

public class Dempsy
extends Object

This class is the master orchestrator of the setup of a VM running the application. It is intended to have the ApplicationDefinitions autowired in so it picks up each one.

Nested Class Summary
 class Dempsy.Application
          There is an instance of an application for every ApplicationDefinition autowired into the Dempsy instance.
